HOUSE BILL No. 1203
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 15-20-5; IC 34-30-2.1-195.2.
Synopsis: Adoption of research animals. Requires research facilities
to offer for adoption dogs or cats no longer required for research
purposes.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Hall, Baird, Miller K
January 5, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Agriculture and Rural
Development.
